thread.title: BRIEF-Votum Q1 Net Profit Down At 1.8 Million Zlotys

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Votum Q1 Net Profit Down At 1.8 Million Zlotys
text:
May 30 (Reuters) - VOTUM SA:
* REPORTED ON TUESDAY Q1 NET PROFIT OF 1.8 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 3.0 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* Q1 REVENUE 26.1 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 24.3 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
